name: The Owner
description:
A portrait of our founder and owner, Dr Volcan Huxley. A self-certified glutton, with a passion for sharing fine delicacies form across the multiverse.

In honor of Dr Huxley's gluttony, the owner of this NFT will receive a copy of every future multi-edition artwork the Teia Cafe produces. The Staff here at the Teia Cafe thanks you for your support.
